For providing an eDIPTFT43 development kit.

FrSky Electronic Co. Ltd. - http://www.frsky-rc.com/
For providing RC telemetry transmitter modules and receivers for development.

Odenwälder Kunststoffwerke Gehäusesysteme GmbH - http://www.okw.com/
For providing enclosure samples for building the prototype.